  <p>We make reasonable efforts to keep information accurate and current, but we cannot guarantee the accuracy of instructions for specific institutions or the continued availability of the processes described. Procedures change. Use this site as a starting point, not a definitive guide.</p>
  <p>The information about debt collectors, consumer rights, and estate obligations is provided for educational purposes. It is not a substitute for legal advice in a specific situation.</p>
  <p>Links to third-party resources — grief support organizations, government agencies, legal aid services — are provided for convenience and are not endorsements. We are not responsible for the content or practices of those sites.</p>
